{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5738201efe","title":"华国锋在湖南长沙发表的声明（大意）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a44c4d5e2e","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"5738201efe"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"70f02a0dc7","name":"资产阶级反动路线","type":"主题"},{"id":"aaf815f20b","name":"华国锋","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"d48f0ea3e8","name":"造反运动和派别斗争","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"be3e4264d6","type":"title","text":"华国锋在湖南长沙发表的声明（大意）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5738201efe"},{"id":"812239200a","type":"paragraph","text":"〖华国锋原是湖南“长高司”的结合对象，是“工联”的对立面。中央点名要湖南省委书记华国锋到北京汇报。十九日在长沙上飞机前，华国锋发表了与以前的观点相反的声明，表示支持“工联”。声明大意如下。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5738201efe"},{"id":"ad876794f2","type":"paragraph","text":"一、自己执行了资产阶级反动路线，愿意悔改，接受群众批判。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5738201efe"},{"id":"fb1808b544","type":"paragraph","text":"二、“长高司”、“红联”、公（安）检（察院）法（院）充当了二月反革命逆流的先锋。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5738201efe"},{"id":"7738a48fb4","type":"paragraph","text":"三、“工联”始终是高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗的，大方向始终是正确的，坚决支持。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5738201efe"},{"id":"c6ecf4d959","type":"paragraph","text":"四、章伯森、梁春阳同志是革命的好干部，要向他们学习。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5738201efe"},{"id":"1b8785102f","type":"paragraph","text":"五、表示了改正错误的决心。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5738201efe"},{"id":"4f2e1c4149","type":"paragraph","text":"（引自清华大学《井冈山通讯》）","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5738201efe"}],"page":{"id":"7874960bf0","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5738201efe","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}